title: Late nights/weekends host Chaz Kangas reflects on The Current's impact locally and beyond

author: The Current
description:
Steve Nelson, The Current's first program director, looks back on launching The Current over the course of six weeks. 

The Current has been an invaluable resource to the music community since it launched in 2005 and it’s all because of you, our incredible community of artists, listeners and members. Thank you.

Find more at thecurrent.org/anniversary
